urce":"rec8N9CvRkM1rJYVY","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec8N9CvRkM1rJYVY","target":"recH5aFqTzpwfDSRi","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec8N9CvRkM1rJYVY","target":"recVMHzYdllgvTo09","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec8N9CvRkM1rJYVY","target":"recEP3QZ3HUmIkv4Q","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec8N9CvRkM1rJYVY","target":"recmL1lWBqWP3mAq3","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec8N9CvRkM1rJYVY","target":"recL1WV82pXaRBQ59","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec8N9CvRkM1rJYVY","target":"recEwQ7ucCWe9yVvi","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec8N9CvRkM1rJYVY","target":"recrwlbTDWOETPpei","label":"event"},{"source":"rec8N9CvRkM1rJYVY","target":"rec70ZLu9pdrEWXR9","label":"event"},{"source":"rec8N9CvRkM1rJYVY","target":"recTplXPehmPfFUiG","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recHrfcCwAN9oOxwj","ref":"Luke.17.1","text":"Then said he unto the disciples, It is impossible but that offences will come: but woe unto him, through whom they come!","year":33},{"id":"recBeqCr9pH6XQWd0","ref":"Luke.17.2","text":"It were better for him that a millstone were hanged about his neck, and he cast into the sea, than that he should offend one of these little ones.","year":33},{"id":"rec9CxKLGXFsVYFWi","ref":"Luke.17.3","text":"Take heed to yourselves: If thy brother trespass against thee, rebuke him; and if he repent, forgive him.","year":33},{"id":"recjOUYdN7EJiBbHR","ref":"Luke.17.4","text":"And if he trespass against thee seven times in a day, and seven times in a day turn again to thee, saying, I repent; thou shalt forgive him.","year":33},{"id":"recQNLWRFQUZVW6Sj","ref":"Luke.17.5","text":"And the apostles said unto the Lord, Increase our faith.","year":33},{"id":"recHxFGvMPafCLscP","ref":"Luke.17.6","text":"And the Lord said, If ye had faith as a grain of mustard seed, ye might say unto this sycamine tree, Be thou plucked up by the root, and be thou planted in the sea; and it should obey you.","year":33},{"id":"recJWq6GM0NE09MGw","ref":"Luke.17.7","text":"But which of you, having a servant plowing or feeding cattle, will say unto him by and by, when he is come from the field, Go and sit down to meat?","year":33},{"id":"reci02TDTPOLzeDh7","ref":"Luke.17.8","text":"And will not rather say unto him, Make ready wherewith I may sup, and gird thyself, and serve me, till I have eaten and drunken; and afterward thou shalt eat and drink?","year":33}]}
